      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 06:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因黑客指控向帕劳发出旅行警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/china-issues-travel-warning-for-palau-following-hack-accusation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几天前，这个太平洋小岛国指责北京参与了一次网络攻击，据称有超过 20,000 份政府文件被盗。此后，中国外交部向帕劳发出了旅行警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/china-issues-travel-warning-for-palau-following-hack-accusation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 04:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
