      <title>七国集团计划如何应对俄罗斯和中国日益增强的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/g7-summit-russia-defense-spending-and-global-south-under-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国及其盟友寻求重新集结对乌克兰的援助，由中国和俄罗斯支持的新伙伴关系正变得更具影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/g7-summit-russia-defense-spending-and-global-south-under-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 04:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
